                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <p> <a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 12 月 12 日消息，苹果今日向 Apple Watch 用户推送了 watchOS 11.2 更新（内部版本号：22S101），本次更新距离上次发布正式版间隔 44 天。</p><p style="text-align: center;"> <img alt="苹果 watchOS 操作系统" height="461" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2022/4/8bd386fb-ecc7-474d-bd95-4c69ba122e7a.jpg?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzEzOC5wbmc=,g_7,x_14,y_14,a_0,t_100" title="苹果 watchOS 11.2 正式发布" width="900" /></p> <p> 需要注意的是，因苹果各区域节点服务器配置缓存问题，可能有些地方探测到升级更新的时间略有延迟，一般半小时内，不会太久。 </p><p> 本文由机器人发布，IT之家稍后将为大家带来具体更新内容。</p> <h3>附 watchOS 11 发布历史：</h3> <ul class="custom_reference"> <li><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/815/685.htm" target="_blank">2024-12-06：watchOS 11.2 RC (22S99)</a></p></li> <li><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/812/061.htm" target="_blank">2024-11-21：watchOS 11.2 Beta 3 (22S5094a)</a></p></li> <li><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/809/816.htm" target="_blank">2024-11-12：watchOS 11.2 Beta 2 (22S5083e)</a></p></li> <li><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/807/898.htm" target="_blank">2024-11-05：watchOS 11.2 Beta (22S5077d)</a></p></li> <li><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/805/956.htm" target="_blank">2024-10-29：watchOS 11.1 (22R585)</a></p></li> <li><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/804/407.htm" target="_blank">2024-10-23：watchOS 11.1 RC (22R582)</a></p></li> <li><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/802/262.htm" target="_blank">2024-10-15：watchOS 11.1 Beta 5 (22R5575a)</a></p></li> <li><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/800/515.htm" target="_blank">2024-10-08：watchOS 11.1 Beta 4 (22R5569a)</a></p></li> <li><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/800/747.htm" target="_blank">2024-10-04：watchOS 11.0.1 (22R361)</a></p></li> <li><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/799/834.htm" target="_blank">2024-1